<div class="accordian-content">
    <h3 class="grab-heading">Insure your vehicle with the company more Kiwis trust</h3>

    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                    <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        Comprehensive Cover
                        <i class="fa fa-angle-down rotate-icon"></i>
                    </button>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                    Full cover for accidental loss or damage to your car as well as accidental damage to someone else’s car. You can choose to have your car repaired by any authorised repair service. At State we have a large network of approved repairers. All repairs done by our approved repairer network is quality guaranteed while you own the car and it's insured with State. We'll cover your legal liability if you accidentally damage someone else’s property or injure someone when you’re driving your car or another vehicle. Provided they’re approved in advance by us, we’ll also cover the costs of your legal defence. Our legal liability also extends to anyone else driving your car - as long as you gave them permission to use it, where they’re not covered by any other insurance, and they meet the same terms of this policy that you must meet.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        Fire, Theft and Third Party Coverage
                        <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                    </button>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                    Cover for loss or damage to your car from fire or theft, plus accidental damage to someone else’s car. All repairs done by our approved repairer network are quality guaranteed as long as you own the car and it’s insured with State. We’ll cover your legal liability if you damage someone else’s property or accidentally injure someone when you’re driving your car or another vehicle. Provided they’re approved in advance by us, we’ll also cover the costs of your legal defence. This cover extends to anyone else driving your car if you gave them permission to use it where they don’t have any other insurance and they meet the same terms of this policy that you must meet.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                <h2 class="mb-0">
                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Third Party Coverage
                        <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
                    </button>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                    Cover for accidental damage to someone else’s car. Your car is covered for up to $3,000 for damage caused by another driver if you can prove it was the other driver’s fault and give us the registration number of the other driver’s vehicle and their identifying information. You’ll also need to help us recover your claim from the driver or the owner of the other driver’s vehicle. If your car isn’t driveable because of damage covered by this policy we’ll pay to get it to a repairer or a safe place.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

